What are you doing?

946
01:37:03,180 --> 01:37:04,270
放開我
Get your hands off me!

947
01:37:04,850 --> 01:37:07,150
拉克哈先生 這是為了你的安全著想
It's all for your own safety, Mr. Lockhart.

948
01:37:07,980 --> 01:37:11,350
