你們要幹嘛?
What are you doing?

1123
01:59:08,400 --> 01:59:09,390
他媽的放開我
Get the fuck off me!

1124
01:59:09,570 --> 01:59:11,470
不...
No. No, no!

1125
01:59:12,010 --> 01:59:13,100
放開我
Get off me.

1126
01:59:13,640 --> 01:59:15,270
救救我 救我
Help me! Help!

1127
01:59:53,650 --> 01:59:55,120
潘柏
Pembroke.

1128
01:59:55,780 --> 01:59:57,150
潘柏先生
Pembroke.

1129
02:00:01,790 --> 02:00:03,620
他們把你怎麼了?
What have they done to you?

1130
02:00:04,460 --> 02:00:05,950
把我怎麼了?
Done to me?

1131
02:00:07,530 --> 02:00:09,520
我從來沒感覺這麼好過
I've never felt better.

1132
02:00:13,840 --> 02:00:15,630
拉克哈先生 放輕鬆
Relax, Mr. Lockhart.

1133
02:00:15,740 --> 02:00:17,140
療程很快就結束了
It'll all be over soon.

1134
02:00:18,810 --> 02:00:21,800
沒錯 了不起的生物
Ah, yes. Remarkable creatures.

1135
02:00:24,650 --> 02:00:29,850
在別的地方 這生物頂多才活十來年
Anywhere else on the planet, this species lives a dozen years, at most.

1136
02:00:30,020 --> 02:00:32,150
但在我們的含水土層裡
Here, in our aquifer...

1137
02:00:33,020 --> 02:00:34,180
它們能活三百年
they can live 300.

1138
02:00:36,360 --> 02:00:38,150
就人類的生理而言
For the human physiology...

1139
02:00:38,330 --> 02:00:42,590
水對人來說挺毒的 你也發現了
the effect of the water can be quite toxic as you have discovered.

1140
02:00:43,730 --> 02:00:46,720
但經過適當的過濾就沒問題了
Unless, of course, it is properly filtered.

1141
02:00:50,170 --> 02:00:52,070
這是男爵發明的療程
The baron devised the process.

1142
02:00:53,510 --> 02:00:57,570
利用他土地所屬的人民實臉
Using the bodies of peasants that belonged to his land...

1143
02:00:58,510 --> 02:01:01,000
他設法將水蒸餾至...
he managed to distill the water...

1144
02:01:01,780 --> 02:01:03,770
活絡生命的精髓
to its life-giving essence.

1145
02:01:06,120 --> 02:01:09,460
他當然為了他的聰明才智 付出慘痛代價
Of course, he paid a terrible price for his ingenuity.

1146
02:01:10,190 --> 02:01:11,180
他唯一的錯...
His only mistake...

1147
02:01:12,190 --> 02:01:14,590
就是利用了非自願的人當對象
was to use subjects who were unwilling.

1148
02:01:15,430 --> 02:01:18,300
幸好 時代不一樣了
Luckily, times have changed.

1149
02:01:21,140 --> 02:01:24,180
這兩百年是人類史上 生產力最旺盛的時期
The last 200 years have been the most productive in human history.

1150
02:01:24,470 --> 02:01:26,800
世人擺脫上帝
Man rid himself of God...

1151
02:01:26,980 --> 02:01:30,070
擺脫階級以及賦予人類意義的一切
of hierarchy, of everything that gave him meaning...

1152
02:01:30,210 --> 02:01:34,080
最後只剩下崇拜自我野心的空虛感
until he was left worshiping the empty altar of his own ambition.

1153
02:01:40,620 --> 02:01:42,210
這是他們來此的原因
That is why they come.

1154
02:01:43,120 --> 02:01:44,220
他們像你一樣
Men like you.

1155
02:01:47,660 --> 02:01:49,390
拉克哈先生 你說得很對
You're quite right, Mr. Lockhart.

1156
02:01:49,560 --> 02:01:50,960
沒有人離開過
No one ever leaves.

1157
02:01:51,400 --> 02:01:54,990
但你搞錯了 是沒人想要離開
What you fail to understand is that no one wants to.

1158
02:02:14,020 --> 02:02:17,250
知道人類困境的療法是什麼嗎?
Do you know what the cure for the human condition is?

1159
02:02:20,260 --> 02:02:21,160
疾病
Disease.

1160
02:02:21,830 --> 02:02:25,430
因為唯有如此才有尋求療法的希望
Because only then is there hope for a cure.

1161
02:03:15,580 --> 02:03:17,310
我不懂
I don't understand.

1162
02:03:17,890 --> 02:03:20,650
多年來 我一在想保護你
For so many years, I've tried to protect you...

1163
02:03:20,820 --> 02:03:23,810
遠離外界的污穢
from the impurities of the outside world.

1164
02:03:24,530 --> 02:03:25,360
但諷刺的是
But ironically, it is your friend Mr. Lockhart

1165
02:03:25,490 --> 02:03:28,520
我們反倒得感謝你朋友拉克哈先生
who we have to thank.

1166
02:03:31,700 --> 02:03:33,000
你現在是女人了
You're a woman now.

1167
02:03:35,100 --> 02:03:36,500
可是我生病了
But I'm not well.

1168
02:03:41,080 --> 02:03:45,070
我永遠都會在這裡照顧你
And I will always be here to take care of you.

1169
02:04:19,580 --> 02:04:20,810
她醒了
She's awake now.

1170
02:04:27,620 --> 02:04:30,420
你讓我以為我有一天會離開這裡
You made me believe I could leave here one day.

1171
02:04:36,300 --> 02:04:38,290
怎麼會有人想要離開?
Why would anybody wanna leave?

1172
02:06:50,100 --> 02:06:52,460
“范海克莫”

1173
02:07:24,430 --> 02:07:25,590
什麼事?
What is it?

1174
02:07:27,000 --> 02:07:27,830
來
Come.

1175
02:07:39,450 --> 02:07:41,110
這是什麼地方?
What is this place?

1176
02:07:45,920 --> 02:07:47,820
這裡就是你生命的起點
This is where you began.

1177
02:08:09,480 --> 02:08:11,270
我不想要
I don't want to.

1178
02:08:17,350 --> 02:08:18,940
你知道...
You know...

1179
02:08:19,120 --> 02:08:22,490
你跟她在新婚之夜一模一樣
you look just like she did on her wedding night.

1180
02:08:22,660 --> 02:08:24,120
“她不曉得”

1181
02:08:27,960 --> 02:08:32,230
村民在那一晚把她從我身邊奪走
The night they took her from me.

1182
02:08:39,510 --> 02:08:43,500
村民挖出胎兒並扔進含水土層
The villagers cut out the fetus and threw it in the aquifer.

1183
02:08:44,710 --> 02:08:46,840
那孩子沒死
The child survived.

1184
02:09:18,280 --> 02:09:20,610
拜託不要 -別怕
Please don't. Don't be frightened.

1185
02:09:20,780 --> 02:09:22,840
我們很快又是一家人了
Soon we'll be a family again.

1186
02:09:23,880 --> 02:09:25,580
這是我們永遠的宿命
The way we were always meant to be.

1187
02:09:41,870 --> 02:09:46,560
沒事 我妹一開始也抗拒過
It's all right. My sister was also somewhat resistant, at first.

1188
02:09:46,560 --> 02:09:50,390
但不久之後 她就愛上了
But after a while, she grew to like it.

1189
02:09:53,610 --> 02:09:57,980
我們不斷努力想製造純潔之物
We tried so many times to make something pure.

1190
02:10:04,060 --> 02:10:06,150
那就是你 我的愛
That something was you, my love.

1191
02:10:10,730 --> 02:10:11,560
現在...
And now...

1192
02:10:13,570 --> 02:10:14,630
我們可以再度開始
we can begin again.

1193
02:10:45,870 --> 02:10:48,100
我等好久了
I've waited so long.

1194
02:11:05,490 --> 02:11:06,950
太久了
So long.

1195
02:11:20,630 --> 02:11:22,730
他會占據你 好嗎?
He will have you. Yes?

1196
02:11:22,900 --> 02:11:23,800
好
Yes.

1197
02:11:38,890 --> 02:11:41,150
你不能永遠把她困在這裡
You can't keep her here forever.

1198
02:11:43,160 --> 02:11:44,090
不能嗎?
No?

1199
02:11:49,030 --> 02:11:51,000
你覺得她到外面會變成什麼樣?
And what do you think would become of her in your world?

1200
02:11:52,830 --> 02:11:54,060
一大堆你們這種人
People like you come to me in droves

1201
02:11:54,170 --> 02:11:56,160
帶著可有可無的生活來找我
with your disposable lives.

1202
02:11:56,940 --> 02:11:58,400
她是你女兒
She's your daughter.

1203
02:12:03,610 --> 02:12:05,440
你又愛過什麼了?
And what have you ever loved, hmm?

1204
02:12:07,010 --> 02:12:09,410
你做過什麼犧牲嗎?
What have you ever sacrificed?

1205
02:12:12,890 --> 02:12:16,450
這就是外面世界的貢獻
This is what the outside world has to offer.

1206
02:12:33,870 --> 02:12:34,900
你說得對
You're right.

1207
02:12:38,280 --> 02:12:39,210
不要
No.

1208
02:13:23,520 --> 02:13:24,580
不要
No.

1209
02:14:06,700 --> 02:14:08,530
失火了
Fire. Fire!

1210
02:15:11,930 --> 02:15:15,370
我經營的一切都是為了她
Everything I have built has been for her.

1211
02:15:19,540 --> 02:15:23,810
你以為我會讓你這種人渣毀了嗎?
You think I would let someone like you destroy that?

1212
02:15:23,980 --> 02:15:25,210
爸
Dad?

1213
02:15:34,420 --> 02:15:35,410
漢娜
Hannah.

1214
02:16:55,640 --> 02:16:59,130
“今日探訪時間已過”

1215
02:17:55,860 --> 02:17:57,920
很壯觀吧?
Magnificent, isn't it?

1216
02:18:08,540 --> 02:18:09,530
拉克哈
Lockhart!

1217
02:18:13,150 --> 02:18:14,580
我們該走了
It's time to go.

1218
02:18:33,100 --> 02:18:35,090
你沒事吧? -老天
- Are you okay? - Jesus Christ.

1219
02:18:36,800 --> 02:18:39,140
別激動
Easy, easy.

1220
02:18:39,740 --> 02:18:40,970
拉克哈?
Lockhart?

1221
02:18:41,140 --> 02:18:42,570
不會吧
My God.

1222
02:18:42,980 --> 02:18:44,470
你做了什麼?
What have you done?

1223
02:18:46,650 --> 02:18:48,440
潘柏呢?
Where's Pembroke?

1224
02:18:50,120 --> 02:18:51,280
他走了
He's gone.

1225
02:18:51,450 --> 02:18:53,010
他走了是什麼意思?
What do you mean "gone"?

1226
02:18:54,150 --> 02:18:55,350
上車
Get in the car.

1227
02:18:59,830 --> 02:19:03,490
你是來辦事的 記得嗎?
You came here to perform a task, remember?

1228
02:19:03,660 --> 02:19:05,830
現在給我上車
Now get in the car.

1229
02:19:09,200 --> 02:19:11,170
你聽到我說的話了嗎?
Did you hear what I said?

1230
02:19:22,680 --> 02:19:24,450
你發瘋了嗎?
Have you lost your mind?

1231
02:19:27,960 --> 02:19:29,350
其實...
Actually...

1232
02:19:31,630 --> 02:19:33,650
我感覺我好多了
I'm feeling much better.

1233
02:19:38,700 --> 02:19:40,690
你搞什麼想去哪?
Where the hell are you going?

1234
02:19:40,870 --> 02:19:44,300
拉克哈 拉克哈
Lockhart! Lockhart!

1235
02:26:21,870 --> 02:26:23,800
翻譯:張倩茜


